JOHN NORTH and IDA RINGLING NORTH, as Executors of the Estate of John Ringling, deceased v. F. H. ALBEE 29 So. (2nd) 371

January Term, 1947

February 28, 1947 Division A Relfearing denied March 27, 1947 John F. Burket, for appellants. Williams & Dart, Attorneys at Law, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

Affirmed. See Section 733.16, Fla. Stats. 1941 (FSA), as amended by Chapters 22783 and 22889, Acts of 1945, Laws of Florida.

THOMAS, C.J., TERRELL and CHAPMAN, JJ., and McNEILL, Associate Justice, concur.
